title: 2014 GSL Season 1 Code A Group B
description:
2014 Global StarCraft II League Season 1/Code A 

Code A, Group A

GSL is a Starcraft 2 tournament organized by the Korean GOM TV 

The videos are HD Rip of the live broadcasts GomEXP / Twitch TV with commentary in English. 


Group B

Lee "Curious" Won Pyo is a Zerg player from South Korea, currently playing for StarTale.[Z]
Hong "Ruin" Deok is a South Korean StarCraft progamer. He plays as Protoss and is currently a member of Incredible Miracle.[P]
Kim "Sleep" Seong Han is a Zerg player from South Korea, who is currently playing for KT Rolster.[Z]
Kim "EffOrt" Jung Woo is a South Korean Brood War and StarCraft II progamer, currently playing for the Korean team CJ Entus.[Z]
